WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.520 --> 00:00:01.600
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.600 --> 00:00:02.617
Praise the Lord.

00:00:02.617 --> 00:00:04.400
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:04.400 --> 00:00:07.120
Well, we're so focused on the war stuff.

00:00:07.120 --> 00:00:14.056
We're so focused on what's going on over there in Israel and all this other stuff that we're forgetting that He said He's going to shake the heavens.

00:00:14.056 --> 00:00:18.011
He's going to shake the earth.

00:00:20.480 --> 00:00:23.280
He's going to shake the politics, and He's going to shake the finances.

00:00:42.580 --> 00:00:42.910
There were five major things He said He was about to shake.

00:00:47.566 --> 00:00:51.933
And I'm telling you all, there's a major earthquake that's about to take place from British Columbia all the way down to about San Francisco.

00:00:51.933 --> 00:00:56.719
I saw a major earthquake that's about to take place there.

00:00:56.719 --> 00:01:01.320
I saw a tsunami wave coming in even into Alaska—something major.

00:01:01.320 --> 00:01:08.150
And I even told everybody what the Lord told me.

00:01:08.150 --> 00:01:11.337
He said, "Watch what's in the water.

00:01:11.337 --> 00:01:18.620
" Many people, because it's out of sight, out of mind, are not paying attention to what's in the water.

00:01:21.167 --> 00:01:25.820
And there will be signs in the days ahead of gases, things, and fish from the depth coming up from the bottom that we've never seen before.

00:01:25.820 --> 00:01:30.240
All around the world, dead fish will come up from the bottom.

00:01:30.240 --> 00:01:31.600
They'll go, "What is this?

00:01:32.667 --> 00:01:32.933
We've never seen it.

00:01:35.659 --> 00:01:43.520
" But it will come up to the top, and things will die on the beaches, and you're going to see things and they'll go, "Where did this come from?

00:01:43.520 --> 00:01:46.289
Where did these whales come from?

00:01:46.289 --> 00:01:48.520
Where's this stuff come from?

00:01:48.520 --> 00:01:57.620
" Because folks, there's stuff that we've never even known existed down there because we've only explored so much of our oceans.

00:01:57.620 --> 00:02:06.079
But I'm telling you by the spirit of the Lord, what He's told me is we're about to see pressure on the earth's crust.

00:02:06.079 --> 00:02:09.359
There's something that's interfering with it in outer space.

00:02:09.359 --> 00:02:20.720
There's something in our galaxy that is interfering with our planet right now that's causing a shifting and a shaking of our earth's crust with the magma and all the lava and all the stuff.

00:02:37.390 --> 00:02:37.620
And I'm telling you, it's the gases; it's all the pressure of the earth.

00:02:38.951 --> 00:02:42.549
And to relieve the pressure from what's happening on our earth's crust, we're going to see earthquakes like we've never seen before.

00:02:48.920 --> 00:02:52.460
And we're going to see volcanoes like we've never even seen before in this generation, up to probably a thousand years.

00:03:08.240 --> 00:03:08.559
I don't know; I just know that this is going to be a worldwide shaking.

00:03:08.559 --> 00:03:13.879
It's not just about America, but it's going to be even about Japan.

00:03:13.879 --> 00:03:15.040
A major earthquake in Japan.

00:03:15.040 --> 00:03:19.259
Major earthquakes in these areas that you go, "Oh my God.

00:03:21.900 --> 00:03:27.493
" And people are going to see it on the news and they're going to wake up the next day, and I saw even 50,000 people in British Columbia die.

00:03:27.493 --> 00:03:28.186
50,000 people.

00:03:30.168 --> 00:03:31.200
I saw the number, and I saw major buildings falling.

00:03:32.777 --> 00:03:33.794
I saw major skyscrapers just tipping over—major shaking.

00:03:34.926 --> 00:03:37.570
And so you say, "Brandon, well, that just scares me.

00:03:37.570 --> 00:03:40.360
" It's not for you to be in fear.

00:03:40.360 --> 00:03:43.360
A thousand shall fall at your side and 10,000 at your right hand.

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:48.799
If you're watching this channel, you're in the right place because I believe in the covenant.

00:03:49.031 --> 00:03:56.340
I believe just like we have these big storms where they say, "Well, they're going to have tornadoes, everything," no, we take authority over tornadoes.

00:03:57.639 --> 00:04:00.709
We don't allow tornadoes around this area.

00:04:02.667 --> 00:04:03.040
We take our authority in this part.

00:04:05.226 --> 00:04:15.120
And I say, "As long as I have dominion and authority—I don't know how far my authority goes out there"—and I'll teach you all this as we go, but you have authority over your neighborhood.

00:04:17.170 --> 00:04:17.990
And that's why I drive around.

00:04:17.990 --> 00:04:22.388
I drive around and pray wherever I put my feet.

00:04:39.760 --> 00:04:40.160
I start pleading the blood and protecting things, going around schools and doing things what God's called me to do to protect.

00:04:40.960 --> 00:04:44.728
I say, "No, we're not going to have any major events or hurting people around here.

00:04:45.816 --> 00:04:46.704
" You moved me to this area.

00:04:47.591 --> 00:04:54.571
I used to do it over where I was in Guthrie, but God said, "I'm moving you out of that area.

00:05:04.080 --> 00:05:04.260
" And He moved us to Tulsa.

00:05:15.131 --> 00:05:15.394
And now we drive around in Tulsa and we pray over the Tulsa area calling for revival.

00:05:15.394 --> 00:05:16.639
We drive around.

00:05:21.320 --> 00:05:22.064
I even go in front of that painting a lot and stay in that neighborhood and pray for revival.

00:05:22.064 --> 00:05:25.919
But I go there because I'm looking for revival.

00:05:25.919 --> 00:05:27.072
It's time to get serious.

00:05:27.072 --> 00:05:33.075
It's time to get serious and expect God to show up and show off in your life.

00:05:33.075 --> 00:05:39.070
It's time to quit playing church, going and having prayer groups and just expecting a normal prayer group.

00:05:41.492 --> 00:05:45.689
I'm talking let the Holy Ghost show up and pray through you so much so that we're changing the nations.

00:05:53.189 --> 00:05:53.440
That's what I pray every single time I do this.

00:05:53.620 --> 00:05:58.160
I said, "God, let it not be me at all, but let You show up.

00:05:58.933 --> 00:06:00.479
" If it's me, I won't put it out.

00:06:16.800 --> 00:06:17.058
I said, "Just erase it, Braden.

00:06:17.058 --> 00:06:18.089
It's just trash.

00:06:18.089 --> 00:06:20.720
" Because if the Holy Spirit isn't there, I'm not there.

00:06:21.093 --> 00:06:22.027
And it's just me making content.

00:06:22.027 --> 00:06:23.956
I'm not here to make content for entertainment.

00:06:29.420 --> 00:06:34.719
If I don't feel a move of the Holy Ghost in a river flow, I'm not releasing it because I'm not here to entertain you.

00:06:34.719 --> 00:06:35.615
We're here to change nations.

00:06:38.319 --> 00:06:38.469
And people say, "Well, just put it out anyway.

00:06:38.469 --> 00:06:39.070
" No, I'm not.

00:06:39.070 --> 00:06:42.669
Like I said, this is a major calling to me.

00:06:42.669 --> 00:06:45.760
This isn't a job; this is a calling.

00:06:55.104 --> 00:06:55.328
And people say, "Well, you know, it's not made for you to understand.

00:06:55.328 --> 00:07:00.328
" This is what God's called me to do, and this is what I'm supposed to do is bring prayer to you.

00:07:00.328 --> 00:07:03.280
And I told Him, I said, "Lord, I'm submitted unto You.

00:07:03.280 --> 00:07:04.868
" So I get still until He speaks.

00:07:05.131 --> 00:07:11.583
I make a video every day, and if I don't feel it, I don't release it.

00:07:11.583 --> 00:07:17.599
If I get up and I tell Brad, "That's trash.

00:07:28.320 --> 00:07:31.712
I'm not releasing that," it's because if I don't feel the power of the Holy Ghost flowing through it, I refuse to waste your time.

00:07:33.640 --> 00:07:38.299
And that's why I feel like people should be at church.

00:07:38.299 --> 00:07:42.160
If you don't feel the Holy Ghost, sit down.

00:07:42.160 --> 00:07:44.663
We've got to get more desperate for Him.

00:08:12.190 --> 00:08:12.500
And in doing so, He will show up.

00:08:12.500 --> 00:08:14.879
He will show up in your desperation.

00:08:21.467 --> 00:08:40.968
I was out power washing the side of my house, and me—I'm going to say this, and you don't know me, but a lot of people think they do—I was power washing my house and I said, "Lord, if I could just have Your help to fix my water line over there, that's all I want to ask You.

00:08:43.395 --> 00:08:44.862
" I was just trying to be humble, like I didn't want to bother Him.

00:08:55.862 --> 00:08:56.137
And He said, "Brandon, I want to be involved in every area of your life.

00:08:57.759 --> 00:09:09.200
Nothing is ever too big and nothing is ever too small for Me to want to be involved with it all.

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:16.331
I want to be involved in every area of your life.

00:09:18.980 --> 00:09:24.470
" In other words, He said to me, "So you think you can do it on your own on the other things?

00:09:24.470 --> 00:09:38.560
" When I was power washing, I said, "Well, I don't really need You to help me power wash the house, but I really need help with that water thing over there.

00:09:38.560 --> 00:09:44.696
" But He said, "You think you can do it on your own?

00:09:45.072 --> 00:09:47.704
You can't do nothing on your own.

00:09:47.704 --> 00:09:58.080
Everything you do, everything you think about, you need Me and you don't even realize it.

00:10:01.519 --> 00:10:02.584
And I'm an ever-present help in a time of need.

00:10:02.584 --> 00:10:12.1000
Everything you do and everything you speak, everything about you, Brandon, you need Me.

00:10:14.679 --> 00:10:25.128
The moment you try to separate yourself from Me is separating yourself from the vine, and there's death in it.

00:10:25.128 --> 00:10:26.312
I am everything.

00:10:26.312 --> 00:10:28.520
I am all in all.

00:10:28.520 --> 00:10:29.839
Do you understand?

00:10:29.839 --> 00:10:34.354
There is nothing that you can do apart from Me, even power washing this house.

00:10:34.354 --> 00:10:36.240
" I started to weep.

00:10:36.660 --> 00:10:40.960
I looked at the ground while I was power washing.

00:10:41.980 --> 00:10:45.870
I was so frustrated that day because we've had a really hard time.

00:10:47.874 --> 00:10:56.453
And I said, "God, help me to never think that I can do anything without You.

00:11:08.190 --> 00:11:11.264
" I didn't want to bother Him, but I said, "Lord, if You could just help me with this water line thing.

00:11:11.576 --> 00:11:14.596
I'm having a real hard time here, and I need help.

00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:16.208
" I can take care of this.

00:11:18.640 --> 00:11:18.840
I can handle it.

00:11:19.840 --> 00:11:26.920
I don't really need you over here on this, but if you could really help me out, just shaking me and making me realize that there's nothing I can do without him.

00:11:26.920 --> 00:11:34.377
Washing a dog, cleaning, mowing my grass whenever it's so high because of all the issues that we've had.

00:11:34.377 --> 00:11:40.514
Walking in every area of your life, being desperate for him to show up in every area.

00:11:40.514 --> 00:11:48.240
Even the things that you don't think that he wants to be involved in, he wants to be involved in.

00:11:57.210 --> 00:11:57.560
It doesn't matter what it is; he wants to be involved in it.

00:11:59.810 --> 00:12:03.040
And that's the place of desperation—allowing the Holy Spirit to move in every area of your life.

00:12:10.399 --> 00:12:10.746
And that's where I was asking him.

00:12:18.320 --> 00:12:18.576
I said, "Oh, so you feel you can do it without me?

00:12:22.320 --> 00:12:25.131
" It checked me really hard because I thought, "Well, of course, I don't need you to power wash the house.

00:12:25.769 --> 00:12:27.769
" And you think you can do it without me?

00:12:27.769 --> 00:12:32.240
In all that you do, in word and in deed, do all for the glory of God.

00:12:32.240 --> 00:12:35.554
All that you do, all for the glory of God.

00:12:51.680 --> 00:12:52.023
I was challenged.

00:12:52.023 --> 00:12:57.800
I listened to what's in these life lessons, you know, with me planting flowers when he said to me, "You just arranged it.

00:12:57.800 --> 00:12:59.200
I caused the flowers to grow.

00:12:59.200 --> 00:13:02.910
I caused the earth to produce and put pressure on the seed.

00:13:02.910 --> 00:13:06.240
I caused the rain to fall on it.

00:13:06.240 --> 00:13:08.994
I was the one that was ahead of all of it, Brandon.

00:13:08.994 --> 00:13:11.392
And all you did was organize them.

00:13:19.520 --> 00:13:19.920
And I even gave you the wisdom to do that.

00:13:19.920 --> 00:13:23.220
" Everything you do, there's nothing apart from me.

00:13:23.220 --> 00:13:25.680
Everything that you do is only through me.

00:13:30.479 --> 00:13:30.959
And in that, I am learning.

00:13:30.959 --> 00:13:33.120
When you think, "I'm a man, I can do this.

00:13:33.120 --> 00:13:34.629
I'm a man, I can fix my car.

00:13:34.629 --> 00:13:39.657
I'm a man, I can mow my grass.

00:13:39.657 --> 00:13:43.600
" It's like, "Daddy, I don't need you to help tie my shoes anymore.

00:13:43.600 --> 00:13:44.507
I'm big now.

00:13:44.693 --> 00:13:46.000
You don't pick out my clothes anymore.

00:13:46.000 --> 00:13:47.839
I can pick my own clothes out, daddy.

00:13:47.839 --> 00:13:54.624
" But even in that, listening to him and saying, "Father, I don't want to get dressed without you.

00:14:07.120 --> 00:14:07.493
What do you feel I should wear today?

00:14:07.493 --> 00:14:12.457
" Involving him in every area of your life.

00:14:12.457 --> 00:14:17.173
"Lord, I need you to tell me how to make my marriage stronger today.

00:14:17.173 --> 00:14:22.350
I need you to tell me how to be a better father to my children.

00:14:24.444 --> 00:14:28.587
" No matter how many books I think I could read or whatever, it all is based solely out of him.

00:14:29.827 --> 00:14:43.698
And I know I don't want to keep going over this, but it's so important that I drive it home to you that he wants to be all in and all to you in every area of your life.

00:14:44.036 --> 00:14:52.089
And so as we see these things in the economy, I told you we do not let up off of things in prayer until we make it a greasy spot.

00:14:59.770 --> 00:15:01.429
You may see a little victory and a lot of people just go, "Well, we saw the first blade, then the ear," and people go, "Well, we can let it go through prayer.

00:15:04.533 --> 00:15:04.818
We don't have to attack it anymore.

00:15:04.818 --> 00:15:11.680
" That's whenever you hit it harder and you hit it until it's a greasy spot.

00:15:11.680 --> 00:15:13.700
So, we see a judge.

00:15:13.700 --> 00:15:14.800
Everything's fine with XRP.

00:15:14.800 --> 00:15:15.714
Everything looks great.

00:15:15.714 --> 00:15:18.114
She goes and starts going against it.

00:15:18.114 --> 00:15:25.799
Instantaneously, people go, "Oh my gosh, the sky is falling with XRP again.

00:15:25.799 --> 00:15:31.360
" And I said, "Isn't it amazing the very things the Lord tells us to pray over?

00:15:48.079 --> 00:15:48.746
" People give up on it and you let go of the rope.

00:15:48.746 --> 00:16:01.760
And then the enemy's there and he's doing tug-of-war and he goes and he tries to pull the rug right out from underneath you instantaneously because the body of Christ goes and pulls and goes, "Look, we won.

00:16:01.760 --> 00:16:02.959
" And then the devil's like...

00:16:02.959 --> 00:16:05.620
and he pulls it and everybody goes, "Well, what happened there?

00:16:08.815 --> 00:16:11.023
" You didn't keep on keeping on.

00:16:22.240 --> 00:16:22.667
You underestimated your enemy.

00:16:22.667 --> 00:16:24.800
And that's what happens.

00:16:30.080 --> 00:16:30.507
It happens a lot with the body of Christ.

00:16:30.507 --> 00:16:35.147
Same thing we do with President Trump.

00:16:35.147 --> 00:16:37.223
We won.

00:16:37.223 --> 00:16:38.491
We won.

00:16:38.491 --> 00:16:39.759
Oh, good.

00:16:39.759 --> 00:16:42.207
We won.

00:16:42.207 --> 00:16:43.600
Oh, November!

00:16:43.600 --> 00:16:44.583
Woohoo!

00:16:54.818 --> 00:16:55.129
And now the Lord starts talking to me and said, "Brandon, are you going to pray for his safety?

00:16:55.129 --> 00:16:57.360
What's going on?

00:16:57.360 --> 00:17:05.817
" There's more things here that you need to understand, that there's more attacks on his life, attempts on his life.

00:17:05.817 --> 00:17:07.348
You need to pray for him.

00:17:07.348 --> 00:17:15.240
So, I'll just be doing my own thing and then the Lord told me, and I see more attempts—like it was with the ear—in the days ahead, worse.

00:17:18.057 --> 00:17:23.319
And we have FBI agents calling 86ing 47, and we see people calling for him to be removed and doing all this stuff.

00:17:23.319 --> 00:17:29.080
Well, I'm just saying I want him to be put in prison.

00:17:29.080 --> 00:17:31.640
That's not what he was saying.

00:17:31.640 --> 00:17:37.740
You have people that are threatening his life on a day-to-day basis, even in upper government.

00:17:37.740 --> 00:17:46.820
And I've told you all, if you don't pray for this man, he can't do it without help.

00:17:46.820 --> 00:17:55.200
No, it's time for the body of Christ to get more serious than what we've ever been serious before.

00:17:55.200 --> 00:17:57.303
And let's drive this thing home.

00:17:57.303 --> 00:17:58.907
Let's finish our race.

00:17:58.907 --> 00:17:59.653
Finish.

00:17:59.653 --> 00:18:00.649
Go long.

00:18:00.649 --> 00:18:02.142
Live long and finish strong.

00:18:02.142 --> 00:18:13.190
We need to live long and finish strong and finish our race with great victory until we get on the other side.

00:18:17.702 --> 00:18:25.640
And when we get over on the other side, then we take a break and we do our victory lap.

00:18:25.640 --> 00:18:27.800
We do our victory lap.

00:18:27.800 --> 00:18:29.440
We do our victory dance.

00:18:29.600 --> 00:18:30.720
I don't know what else to say.

00:18:30.720 --> 00:18:32.468
But until then, we are on battle mode.

00:18:32.468 --> 00:18:34.736
We've got our shield up.

00:18:34.736 --> 00:18:41.737
We're not looking at our enemy and going, "Well, he's already lost.

00:18:41.737 --> 00:18:44.440
" Yeah, he's already lost.

00:18:44.440 --> 00:18:56.937
But we stay in a state of war with our sword and our shield in our hand going, "Hey, where's another devil?

00:18:56.937 --> 00:19:02.011
I'm going to cut this devil's head off and I'm going to keep warring against him.

00:19:02.011 --> 00:19:10.480
" Because the moment you take your eye off your enemy, he's there ready to devour you.

00:19:20.720 --> 00:19:20.970
That's just the end times.

00:19:20.970 --> 00:19:21.220
You know why?

00:19:21.220 --> 00:19:22.720
Let me tell you why.

00:19:27.680 --> 00:19:28.000
Because he has a sense of urgency.

00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:29.554
What's his urgency?

00:19:33.879 --> 00:19:34.219
He knows his time is short.

00:19:38.011 --> 00:19:38.263
He has a sense of urgency.

00:19:49.599 --> 00:19:49.919
So where's the body of Christ's urgency right now?

00:19:49.919 --> 00:20:01.200
Well, you know, it's not convenient to go to prayer group on Sunday nights after church.

00:20:01.200 --> 00:20:07.400
So you have, you know, 20 people show up out of a church of over a thousand.

00:20:20.743 --> 00:20:21.120
That is pathetic.

00:20:21.120 --> 00:20:25.019
Where's the sense of urgency?

00:20:25.019 --> 00:20:41.248
You have the elders; you have the gray hairs in there—the people who are the pillars of the church that have been there—but the young people, they don't care.

00:20:43.264 --> 00:20:43.552
"I got to watch American Idol.

00:20:43.552 --> 00:20:44.860
" Do you understand?

00:20:44.860 --> 00:20:53.520
If we do not pray it out in the spirit, it will never happen in the natural.

00:20:53.520 --> 00:21:00.159
You think that you get spiritual breakthrough just because it's just supposed to happen?

00:21:00.159 --> 00:21:03.657
It happens birthed out of the spirit first.

00:21:03.657 --> 00:21:04.846
Healings, demonstrations, manifestation.

00:21:04.846 --> 00:21:09.120
Azusa Street came out of major prayer first.

00:21:09.120 --> 00:21:15.840
Pensacola revival of John Kilpatrick came out of two years of intercessory prayer.

00:21:15.840 --> 00:21:17.200
Two years of praying.

00:21:17.200 --> 00:21:27.977
I don't know if it was twice a week or once a week, but they prayed and they did that for two years, and then on Father's Day, bam, the glory fell.

00:21:27.977 --> 00:21:29.810
Two years they prayed for revival.

00:21:29.810 --> 00:21:40.660
Azusa Street, I think it was like four years; William Seymour and them, they prayed in a little house.

00:21:40.660 --> 00:21:45.280
They prayed and prayed and prayed, and then God gave them a word.

00:21:51.212 --> 00:21:59.759
There was a great earthquake and it shook San Francisco, and then because they gave that prophetic word, people were going, "Who gave that accurate prophetic word?

00:22:03.817 --> 00:22:05.051
" and the glory showed up and they had to move it into a barn.

00:22:05.051 --> 00:22:08.667
God will show up in the most unlikely places.

00:22:17.328 --> 00:22:17.600
He shows up in a place of desperation.

00:22:18.590 --> 00:22:25.040
He shows up with the people who are desperate and hungry.

00:22:25.040 --> 00:22:27.460
He'll show up in a stable.

00:22:27.460 --> 00:22:34.799
Remember, he'll show up in a stable in a place where barn animals are—not fit for a king.

00:22:34.799 --> 00:22:39.600
But he shows up in a place of humility, not a place of arrogance.

00:22:44.604 --> 00:22:48.571
People who are arrogant leading prayer, people who are arrogant preaching at the church thinking, "Well, I've got my PhD.

